020package org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer;
021
022import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.DEPRECATED;
023import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.STABLE;
024
025import java.lang.reflect.ParameterizedType;
026import java.lang.reflect.Type;
027import java.util.LinkedHashMap;
028import java.util.List;
029
030import org.apiguardian.api.API;
031import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
032import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.internal.ParameterizedTypeNameImpl;
033
034/**
035 *  The specialisation of
036 *  {@link TypeName}
037 *  for parameterised types.
038 *
039 *  @author Square,Inc.
040 *  @modified Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
041 *  @version $Id: ParameterizedTypeName.java 943 2021-12-21 01:34:32Z tquadrat $
042 *  @since 0.0.5
043 *
044 *  @UMLGraph.link
045 */
046@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: ParameterizedTypeName.java 943 2021-12-21 01:34:32Z tquadrat $" )
047@API( status = STABLE, since = "0.0.5" )
048public sealed interface ParameterizedTypeName extends TypeName
049    permits ParameterizedTypeNameImpl
050{
051        /*---------*\
052    ====** Methods **==========================================================
053        \*---------*/
054    /**
055     *  {@inheritDoc}
056     */
057    @Override
058    public ParameterizedTypeName annotated( final List<AnnotationSpec> annotations );
059
060    /**
061     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
062     *  given raw type.
063     *
064     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
065     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
066     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
067     */
068    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
069    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
070    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final Class<?> rawType, final Type... typeArguments )
071    {
072        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( rawType, typeArguments );
073
074        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
075        return retValue;
076    }   //  from()
077
078    /**
079     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
080     *  given raw type.
081     *
082     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
083     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
084     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
085     */
086    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
087    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
088    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final ClassName rawType, final TypeName... typeArguments )
089    {
090        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( rawType, typeArguments );
091
092        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
093        return retValue;
094    }   //  from()
095
096    /**
097     *  Returns a parameterised type equivalent to the given type.
098     *
099     *  @param  type    The other type.
100     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
101     */
102    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
103    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
104    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final ParameterizedType type )
105    {
106        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( type, new LinkedHashMap<>() );
107
108        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
109        return retValue;
110    }   //  from()
111
112    /**
113     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
114     *  given raw type.
115     *
116     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
117     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
118     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
119     *
120     *  @deprecated Use
121     *      {@link #from(Class, Type...)}
122     *      instead.
123     */
124    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
125    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
126    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
127    public static ParameterizedTypeName get( final Class<?> rawType, final Type... typeArguments )
128    {
129        final var retValue = from( rawType, typeArguments );
130
131        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
132        return retValue;
133    }   //  get()
134
135    /**
136     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
137     *  given raw type.
138     *
139     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
140     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
141     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
142     *
143     *  @deprecated Use
144     *      {@link #from(ClassName, TypeName...)}
145     *      instead.
146     */
147    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
148    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
149    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
150    public static ParameterizedTypeName get( final ClassName rawType, final TypeName... typeArguments )
151    {
152        final var retValue = from( rawType, typeArguments );
153
154        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
155        return retValue;
156    }   //  get()
157
158    /**
159     *  Returns a parameterised type equivalent to the given type.
160     *
161     *  @param  type    The other type.
162     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
163     *
164     *  @deprecated Use
165     *      {@link #from(ParameterizedType)}
166     *      instead.
167     */
168    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
169    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
170    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
171    public static ParameterizedTypeName get( final ParameterizedType type ) { return from( type ); }
172
173    /**
174     *  Returns a new {@code ParameterizedTypeName} instance for the specified
175     *  name as nested inside this class.
176     *
177     *  @param  name    The name for the nested class.
178     *  @return The new nested class.
179     */
180    public ParameterizedTypeName nestedClass( final CharSequence name );
181
182    /**
183     *  Returns a new {@code ParameterizedTypeName} instance for the specified
184     *  name as nested inside this class, with the specified type arguments.
185     *
186     *  @param  name    The name for the nested class.
187     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
188     *  @return The new nested class.
189     */
190    public ParameterizedTypeName nestedClass( final CharSequence name, final List<TypeName> typeArguments );
191
192    /**
193     *  Returns the raw type for this parameterised type name.
194     *
195     *  @return The raw type.
196     */
197    public ClassName rawType();
198
199    /**
200     *  Returns the type arguments for this parameterised type name.
201     *
202     *  @return The type arguments.
203     */
204    public List<? extends TypeName> typeArguments();
205
206    /**
207     *  {@inheritDoc}
208     */
209    @SuppressWarnings( "AbstractMethodOverridesAbstractMethod" )
210    @Override
211    public TypeName withoutAnnotations();
212}
213//  interface ParameterizedTypeName
214
